# Class: pbpko:OBI_0000571 (manufacturer role)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0000571 "Manufacturer role is a role which inheres in a person or organization and which is realized by a manufacturing process."@en)
