# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200033 (leave one out cross validation method)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200033 "is a data transformation :  leave-one-out cross-validation (LOOCV) involves using a single observation from the original sample as the validation data, and the remaining observations as the training data. This is repeated such that each observation in the sample is used once as the validation data"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200033 "Person:Helen Parkinson")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200033 "leave one out cross validation method"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200033 pbpko:OBI_0000792)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200033 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000417 pbpko:OBI_0200188))

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200041 (k-means clustering)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200041 "A k-means clustering is a data transformation which achieves a class discovery or partitioning objective, which takes as input a collection of objects (represented as points in multidimensional space) and which partitions them into a specified number k of clusters. The algorithm attempts to find the centers of natural clusters in the data. The most common form of the algorithm starts by partitioning the input points into k initial sets, either at random or using some heuristic data. It then calculates the mean point, or centroid, of each set. It constructs a new partition by associating each point with the closest centroid. Then the centroids are recalculated for the new clusters, and the algorithm repeated by alternate applications of these two steps until convergence, which is obtained when the points no longer switch clusters (or alternatively centroids are no longer changed)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200041 "Elisabetta Manduchi")
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200041 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200041 "Philippe Rocca-Serra")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200041 "k-means clustering"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200041 pbpko:OBI_0200171)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200041 pbpko:OBI_0200175)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200041 ObjectIntersectionOf(ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000299 pbpko:OBI_0000648) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000417 pbpko:OBI_0200178)))
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200041 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000417 pbpko:OBI_0200172))

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200042 (hierarchical clustering)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200042 "A hierarchical clustering is a data transformation which achieves a class discovery objective, which takes as input data item and builds a hierarchy of clusters. The traditional representation of this hierarchy is a tree (visualized by a dendrogram), with the individual input objects at one end (leaves) and a single cluster containing every object at the other (root)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200042 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200042 "hierarchical clustering"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200042 pbpko:OBI_0200175)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200042 ObjectIntersectionOf(ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000299 pbpko:OBI_0000648) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000417 pbpko:OBI_0200178)))

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200050 (dimensionality reduction)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200050 "A dimensionality reduction is data partitioning which transforms each input m-dimensional vector (x_1, x_2, ..., x_m) into an output n-dimensional vector (y_1, y_2, ..., y_n), where n is smaller than m."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200050 "Elisabetta Manduchi"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200050 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200050 "Melanie Courtot"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200050 "Philippe Rocca-Serra")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200050 "dimensionality reduction"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200050 pbpko:OBI_0200175)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200050 ObjectIntersectionOf(ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000299 pbpko:OBI_0000648) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000417 pbpko:OBI_0200178)))

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200051 (principal components analysis dimensionality reduction)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200051 "A principal components analysis dimensionality reduction is a dimensionality reduction achieved by applying principal components analysis and by keeping low-order principal components and excluding higher-order ones."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200051 "Elisabetta Manduchi"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200051 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200051 "Melanie Courtot"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200051 "Philippe Rocca-Serra")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200051 "principal components analysis dimensionality reduction"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200051 pbpko:OBI_0200050)

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200111 (data visualization)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200111 "A planned process with the objective to graphically represent some data by inputing the data and outputting images, diagrams or animations."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200111 "Elisabetta Manduchi"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200111 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200111 "Melanie Courtot"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200111 "Tina Boussard"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200111 "data visualization"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200111 pbpko:COB_0000035)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200111 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000293 pbpko:IAO_0000027))
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200111 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000299 ObjectUnionOf(pbpko:IAO_0000038 pbpko:IAO_0000101)))
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200111 ObjectAllValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000293 pbpko:IAO_0000027))
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200111 ObjectAllValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000299 ObjectUnionOf(pbpko:IAO_0000038 pbpko:IAO_0000101)))

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200166 (data transformation objective)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200166 "An objective specification to transformation input data into output data"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200166 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200166 "data transformation objective"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200166 pbpko:IAO_0000005)

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200171 (partitioning data transformation)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200171 "A partitioning data transformation is a data transformation that has objective partitioning."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200171 "James Malone")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200171 "partitioning data transformation"@en)
EquivalentClasses(pbpko:OBI_0200171 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000417 pbpko:OBI_0200172))
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200171 pbpko:OBI_0200000)

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200172 (partitioning objective)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200172 "A partitioning objective is a data transformation objective where the aim is to generate a collection of disjoint non-empty subsets whose union equals a non-empty input set."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200172 "Elisabetta Manduchi")
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200172 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200172 "partitioning objective"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200172 pbpko:OBI_0200166)

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200175 (class discovery data transformation)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200175 "A class discovery data transformation (sometimes called unsupervised classification) is a data transformation that has objective class discovery."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200175 "James Malone")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200175 "class discovery data transformation"@en)
EquivalentClasses(pbpko:OBI_0200175 ObjectUnionOf(ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000299 pbpko:OBI_0000648) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000417 pbpko:OBI_0200178)))
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200175 pbpko:OBI_0200000)

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200178 (class discovery objective)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200178 "A class discovery objective (sometimes called unsupervised classification) is a data transformation objective where the aim is to organize input data  (typically vectors of attributes) into classes, where the number of classes and their specifications are not known a priori. Depending on usage, the class assignment can be definite or probabilistic."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200178 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200178 "class discovery objective"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200178 pbpko:OBI_0200166)

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200179 (class prediction objective)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200179 "A class prediction objective (sometimes called supervised classification) is a data transformation objective where the aim is to create a predictor from training data through a machine learning technique. The training data consist of pairs of objects (typically vectors of attributes) and
class labels for these objects. The resulting predictor can be used to attach class labels to any valid novel input object. Depending on usage, the prediction can be definite or probabilistic. A classification is learned from the training data and can then be tested on test data."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200179 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200179 "class prediction objective"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200179 pbpko:OBI_0200166)

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200188 (cross validation objective)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200188 "A cross validation objective is a data transformation objective in which the aim is to partition a sample of data into subsets such that the analysis is initially performed on a single subset, while the other subset(s) are retained for subsequent use in confirming and validating the initial analysis."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200188 "James Malone"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200188 "cross validation objective"@en)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200188 pbpko:OBI_0200172)

# Class: pbpko:OBI_0200190 (clustered data visualization)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0200190 "A data visualization which has input of a clustered data set and produces an output of a report graph which is capable of rendering data of this type."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0200190 "James Malone")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:OBI_0200190 "clustered data visualization")
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200190 pbpko:OBI_0200111)
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200190 ObjectSomeValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000299 ObjectUnionOf(pbpko:IAO_0000037 pbpko:IAO_0000179 pbpko:IAO_0000180 pbpko:IAO_0000183 pbpko:IAO_0000184)))
SubClassOf(pbpko:OBI_0200190 ObjectAllValuesFrom(pbpko:OBI_0000293 pbpko:OBI_0000648))

